{"tid":44364,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"達哥最後一集直播打機？幾張揮春收佢皮","createTime":"2016-12-18T08:23:46.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-18T10:41:00.000Z","uid":49391,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"05cea33c7a0b5d5e90b50ba2fa4c89df6c90ac15","tid":44364,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T08:23:46.000Z","msg":"本地著名Twitcher林慧韡（達哥）經常直播打機片段，最近埋首直播今年11月發行的《Watch Dog2》，遊戲以黑客為主題，背景為虛構的美國三藩市。遊戲中有不同任務，達哥在11月29日直播片段中控制遊戲中角色進入一間中式餐廳，場景內櫃台附近發現有數張揮春，達哥利用遊戲中手機拍照模式放大畫面，竟看到揮春寫有「我要真普選」，達哥表示「呢度有把遮喎，咁過癮嘅」，看到左面另一張寫有「冚家富貴」，達哥即指「嘩呢個仲痴線」；移至右邊，更有一張「毋忘六四」。<br />\n<br />\n達哥笑謂「點解有人寫呢啲做揮春」，並笑言「戴頭盔，呢啲言論唔代表本人立場」，「咁得意嘅，你哋睇到啲咩就睇到啲咩啦」，一邊稱「我就睇到無字天書」一邊為「毋忘六四」揮春拍照，並再為其他揮春逐一拍照。<br />\n<br />\n不少觀看直播人士隨即在留言表示要立刻入手該遊戲，「要買Watch Dog了」、「8964」、「好正」、「反了反了」；有人笑指「達哥，你聽日唔駛開台了」、「公安拍門」、「要被失蹤了」，有人亦預言該遊戲將被內地禁售。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20161202/19852839\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20161202%2F19852839&d=LuN311ryFqadCm5aAoakJwT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=a27ce0fa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20161202%2F19852839&h=c9bb25a8\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20161202/19852839</a>"},{"pid":"886c41a3ca94da5416b1bbdc1b2b7ec55ef637f0","tid":44364,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T08:24:20.000Z","msg":"IMOM"},{"pid":"3f040a5c9f35147b2152026afca41adc4dc436cb","tid":44364,"uid":22313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T08:37:34.000Z","msg":"old news is so"},{"pid":"093b87dcab2b99372133abaceedb26de2236b354","tid":44364,"uid":17914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T10:36:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9146dc17bb6a4e62e5261c9be104435d37fa7994","tid":44364,"uid":3818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T10:39:19.000Z","msg":"Wow"},{"pid":"d958e9fe97fc255a113abd012dfda9b50010dc5e","tid":44364,"uid":2739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T10:41:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4208S0v.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4208S0v.png&h=6dd1d6de&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}